OL,3,CEfforts to stamp out drugs in prison
OL,4,Conly 'dressing the wounds'
OL,6,FMr Thompson, who was himself sentenced
OL,7,Ffor drug dealing, said such
OL,8,Finitiatives were not dealing with the
OL,9,Froot causes.
OL,11,F"From the perspective of the prisons,
OL,12,Fthey need to be seen to be doing
OL,13,Fsomething," he said.
OL,15,F"But it is only dressing the wounds,
OL,16,Fit's not getting to the core of the
OL,17,Fissue.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
