OL,3,CEfforts to stamp out drugs in prison
OL,4,Conly 'dressing the wounds'
OL,6,F"I think until those needs are met,
OL,7,Fthe demand on the prison service, or
OL,8,Fthe burden on the prison service to
OL,9,Fdeal with issues around drugs and
OL,10,Fviolence from drugs and anti social
OL,11,Fbehaviour, will only carry on."
OL,13,F'Zero tolerance approach'
OL,15,FThis year alone, HMP Doncaster has
OL,16,Fcaught 41 prisoners attempting to
OL,17,Fsmuggle contraband into prison when
OL,18,Fthey have arrived as new inmates.
