OL,3,CEfforts to stamp out drugs in prison
OL,4,Conly 'dressing the wounds'
OL,6,FMr Thompson said illegal substances
OL,7,Finside were commonplace. He said:
OL,8,F"During my first week in prison,
OL,9,Fwithin the first few days I
OL,10,Fexperienced seeing a parcel of illicit
OL,11,Fitems being thrown over the fence into
OL,12,Fthe yard.
OL,14,F"Just like that you can see just how
OL,15,Feasy it is to get these illicit items
OL,16,Fto make their way into a secure
OL,17,Fenvironment like that."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
