OL,3,CEfforts to stamp out drugs in prison
OL,4,Conly 'dressing the wounds'
OL,6,FRachel Barras, deputy director at HMP
OL,7,FDoncaster, said: "We have a zero
OL,8,Ftolerance approach to drugs in
OL,9,Fprisons, because that can fuel
OL,10,Fviolence, bullying, and it puts both
OL,11,Fprisoners and staff at risk."
